## Responsive Design

### Breakpoints
- Mobile-first approach (default styles for mobile)
- Tablet: `48rem` (768px) - use `@media (min-width: 48rem)`
- Desktop: `64rem` (1024px) - use `@media (min-width: 64rem)`
- Large Desktop: `80rem` (1280px) - use `@media (min-width: 80rem)`

**Note:** CSS variables cannot be used in `@media` queries, so use the values directly with comments:
```css
@media (min-width: 48rem) {  /* --breakpoint-md */
  /* Tablet styles */
}
```

## Accessibility Requirements

### Focus States
- Always include: Yellow outline (`--color-primary-yellow`)
- Adequate offset (`--outline-offset-sm`)
- Visible on all interactive elements

### Touch Targets
- Minimum size: `var(--touch-target-min)` (2.75rem/44px)
- Ensure buttons and links have sufficient clickable area

### Keyboard Navigation
- All interactive elements must be keyboard accessible
- Logical tab order
- Skip links for main content
- ARIA labels where needed

## Button Guidelines

### Primary Button (`.btn-primary`)
- Use for: Main call-to-action, primary user actions
- Black background (`--color-primary-black`), white text
- Focus: Yellow outline

### Secondary Button (`.btn-secondary`)
- Use for: Secondary actions, alternative options
- Transparent background, black text, gray border
- Focus: Yellow outline

## Card Guidelines

### Content Cards (`.card`)
- White background
- Use for: Content previews, feature highlights, grid layouts
- Hover: Slight lift, enhanced shadow
- Focus: Yellow outline

### Related Results Cards (`.related-card`)
- Use for: Related content on detail pages
- Icon/image at top, heading, list of items
- 3-column grid on desktop

## Typography Guidelines

### Font Sizes
- **5xl (3rem)**: Hero titles, landing page main headings
- **4xl (2.25rem)**: Section titles, major page headings
- **3xl (1.875rem)**: Subsection headings, large content titles
- **2xl (1.5rem)**: Medium headings, section subheadings
- **xl (1.25rem)**: Small headings, card titles
- **lg (1.125rem)**: Large body text, emphasized content
- **base (1rem)**: Default body text, buttons, form inputs
- **sm (0.875rem)**: Small text, captions, metadata
- **xs (0.75rem)**: Tiny text, fine print

### Font Weights
- **Extrabold (800)**: Hero titles, major emphasis
- **Bold (700)**: Section headings, important content
- **Semibold (600)**: Buttons, card titles, emphasized text
- **Medium (500)**: Navigation links, subheadings
- **Normal (400)**: Body text, default weight

## Layout Patterns

### Containers
- `.landing-container`: Landing page sections (max-width: 75rem)
- `.record-container`: Individual record pages (max-width: 80rem)
- `.search-section`: Search page content (max-width: 72.5rem)

### Grids
- `.cards-grid`: 3-column grid, stacks to 1 column on mobile
- Gap: `--spacing-8`

