## Quick Reference

### Common Mistakes to Avoid
1. ‚ùå Hardcoding CSS values instead of using tokens
2. ‚ùå Using `px` for spacing/fonts instead of `rem` via tokens
3. ‚ùå Defining custom values in component CSS files
4. ‚ùå Importing CSS files in wrong order
5. ‚ùå Using inline styles
6. ‚ùå Creating components without checking existing patterns
7. ‚ùå Not including accessibility features (focus states, ARIA)
8. ‚ùå Making touch targets too small (< 44px)

